YOU KILLED MY WIFE!

37:58.917 --> 38:02.208
♪♪♪

38:02.250 --> 38:06.083
(man)
♪ I GET COLD IN THE QUIET ♪

38:07.709 --> 38:12.291
♪ GUESS THE SOUND IS ASLEEP ♪

38:12.333 --> 38:15.000
♪ THE NIGHT IS YOUNG ♪

38:15.041 --> 38:18.166
♪ AND IT'S COMFORTING ♪

38:20.834 --> 38:25.166
♪ SO BRING ON THE FIGHT ♪

38:25.208 --> 38:29.500
♪ AND THE WEIGHT OF LOVE ♪

38:29.542 --> 38:34.041
♪ AND THE MISDIRECTION
OF THIS HOLY DOVE ♪

38:34.083 --> 38:37.166
I, UH, OWE YOU AN APOLOGY.

38:37.208 --> 38:40.667
SOME THINGS ARE HARD
TO ACCEPT, RIGHT? I GET THAT.

38:40.709 --> 38:43.125
YOU KNOW, BEFORE YESTERDAY,
I NEVER STRUCK ANOTHER PERSON.

38:43.166 --> 38:45.041
OH, YEAH?

38:45.083 --> 38:48.542
WELL, NOT A BAD RIGHT CROSS
FOR A SHRINK.

38:48.583 --> 38:51.041
THANK YOU.

38:51.083 --> 38:54.375
♪ WHEN YOU'RE DOWN
ON YOUR KNEES ♪

38:56.375 --> 39:00.250
♪ AND I STILL CAN'T REMEMBER ♪

39:00.291 --> 39:05.041
♪ THE WARMTH OF SEPTEMBER ♪

39:05.083 --> 39:08.208
♪ THE SAME STARS
THAT COVER YOU ♪

39:08.250 --> 39:10.166
♪ THEY COVER ME ♪

39:10.208 --> 39:12.917
PETE.

39:12.959 --> 39:14.583
I'LL BE RIGHT IN.

39:14.625 --> 39:18.500
♪♪♪

39:18.542 --> 39:20.500
I'M TIRED OF MAKING
THE WRONG CHOICES.

39:20.542 --> 39:22.041
I'VE DONE THAT TOO MUCH.

39:22.083 --> 39:24.041
I WANT TO MAKE
THE RIGHT CHOICE.

39:24.083 --> 39:26.250
WHAT ARE YOU SAYING?

39:26.291 --> 39:30.041
MAYBE I COULD BE
IN LOVE WITH YOU, TOO.

39:30.083 --> 39:32.125
(exhales)

39:32.166 --> 39:33.375
YEAH?

39:33.417 --> 39:35.166
YEAH.

39:38.083 --> 39:41.041
♪♪♪

39:41.083 --> 39:43.750
I WANTED TO APOLOGIZE
FOR LAST NIGHT.

39:43.792 --> 39:46.041
IT WAS JUVENILE.
I WAS JUVENILE.

39:46.083 --> 39:49.041
AND I COULD LIE AND BLAME IT
ON ENDORPHINS FROM A FIGHT.

39:49.083 --> 39:50.250
BUT... (stammers)

39:50.291 --> 39:54.041
IT WAS JUST ME BEING STUPID
AND INSECURE.

39:54.083 --> 39:57.083
I MEAN, YOU KNOW, A BEAUTIFUL
WOMAN LIKE YOU, I WASN'T SURE--

39:57.125 --> 39:58.625
SHELDON.
YEAH.

39:58.667 --> 40:00.750
SHUT UP.

40:02.417 --> 40:07.417
♪ YOU'RE THE PATH ♪

40:07.458 --> 40:10.250
(knock on door)

40:10.291 --> 40:14.041
I HEARD ABOUT KAYLA.

40:14.083 --> 40:16.041
YOU OKAY?

40:16.083 --> 40:18.041
THIS IS ME, GLOATING.

40:18.083 --> 40:23.083
♪ YOU STILL CAN'T REMEMBER ♪

40:23.125 --> 40:26.166
MM.

40:26.208 --> 40:28.917
♪ ...OF SEPTEMBER ♪

40:28.959 --> 40:31.750
I'M SORRY.

40:31.792 --> 40:33.917
ME, TOO.

40:33.959 --> 40:37.041
I REALLY AM, SAM.

40:37.083 --> 40:39.709
BEING RIGHT
IS ALL WELL AND GOOD,

40:39.750 --> 40:44.041
BUT IT'S NOT... MUCH FUN.

40:44.083 --> 40:46.417
HOW'S VANESSA?

40:46.458 --> 40:48.667
SHE'S ALL RIGHT.

40:48.709 --> 40:50.667
GOOD.

40:50.709 --> 40:54.333
SHE MADE A BAD CALL.
WE ALL MAKE BAD CALLS.

40:54.375 --> 40:56.125
YEAH.

40:56.166 --> 40:57.834
♪♪♪

40:57.875 --> 41:02.041
YOU AND I
WERE A BAD CALL.

41:02.083 --> 41:04.792
(exhales) YEAH.

41:04.834 --> 41:08.291
♪♪♪

41:08.333 --> 41:10.959
TALKED TO PETE.

41:13.083 --> 41:16.041
DID YOU TELL HIM THAT YOU
WANTED TO BE WITH HIM?

41:16.083 --> 41:18.041
YEAH, I'M JUST...
WE'RE JUST GONNA TRY,

41:18.083 --> 41:20.583
YOU KNOW, WE'RE GONNA
SEE IF IT WORKS...

41:20.625 --> 41:22.500
ATTEMPT TO BE HAPPY.

41:22.542 --> 41:24.667
THAT'S GOOD.

41:24.709 --> 41:29.041
I'M TRYING
TO GROW THE HELL UP, SAM.

41:29.083 --> 41:31.125
♪♪♪

41:31.166 --> 41:33.667
I WANT YOU TO BE HAPPY.

41:33.709 --> 41:35.709
I WANT YOU
TO BE HAPPY, TOO.

41:35.750 --> 41:38.500
♪ I LIE ALONE ♪

41:38.542 --> 41:41.166
♪ JUST BARE FLESH ♪

41:41.208 --> 41:43.917
♪ BARE AT BONE ♪

41:43.959 --> 41:45.834
ADDISON.

41:48.041 --> 41:51.125
I WAS COMING UP HERE TO...

41:51.166 --> 41:52.834
TELL YOU WHAT HAPPENED
TO ME TODAY,

41:52.875 --> 41:56.041
BUT IT SEEMS LIKE ALL
THE REAL ACTION IS UP HERE.

41:56.083 --> 41:59.041
NO, NO. NAI, NOT AT ALL.
NOTHING EVER HAPPENED.

41:59.083 --> 42:01.667
♪♪♪

42:01.709 --> 42:05.041
WE...

42:05.083 --> 42:07.834
WE KISSED, NAI,
BUT YOU HAVE TO BELIEVE ME

42:07.875 --> 42:10.959
WHEN I TELL...

42:11.000 --> 42:13.834
SHAME ON YOU.

42:13.875 --> 42:19.041
♪ OH ♪

42:19.083 --> 42:22.041
♪ OH ♪

